# Windows build outputs are NOT checked in - the self-contained pype.exe is
# ~150MB and PypeSetup.exe ~63MB, both over GitHub's 100MB hard push limit
# (the first would outright fail to push). Build them locally instead: see
# windows/README.md ("Building"). mac/dist/ is the opposite case - pype.app
# and PypeInstaller.pkg are only a few hundred KB (Swift dynamically links
# system frameworks rather than bundling a runtime), so those ARE checked in
# for "ready to install immediately" convenience.
/windows/dist/
/windows/installer/pype.exe
*.user
.DS_Store
.build/
.swiftpm/

# Claude Code's own local session/tool state - not part of the project.
.claude/
